summary: OSB GROUP PLC ISIN: GB00BLDRH36019 February 2026 LEI number: 213800ZBKL9BHSL2K459 OSB GROUP PLC (the “Company”) Transaction in Own Shares The Company announces that on 18 February 2026 it had purchased a total of 69,180 of its ordinary shares of £0.01 each (the "ordinary shares") on the London Stock Exchange, CBOE BXE and CBOE CXE, through the Company's broker Citigroup Global Markets Limited as detailed below. headline: Kurv Launches KCOP: A New Way of Seeking Enhanced Income With Copper
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, February 19, 2026--Kurv Investment Management, a provider of tax-efficient, alternative strategies, today announced the launch of the Kurv Copper & Mining Enhanced Income ETF (CBOE BXZ: KCOP). KCOP aims to offer investors enhanced income while outperforming the price return of copper and copper mining equities.
